---
import IndustriesAccordion from './IndustriesAccordion';
---

<section class="py-20 px-6 bg-page-bg border-t border-white/[0.05]" id="industries">
  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p
        class="uppercase text-xs font-bold tracking-[3px] text-accent mb-3"
        data-anim="fade-up"
      >
        Who We Serve
      </p>
      <h2
        class="text-[1.85rem] md:text-[3rem] font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight tracking-tight font-serif"
        data-anim="fade-up"
        style="transition-delay: 100ms"
      >
        Built for Real Operators
      </h2>
      <div class="w-16 h-[3px] bg-accent mx-auto mb-4 divider-animate"></div>
      <p
        class="text-xl text-white/60 max-w-[640px] mx-auto leading-relaxed"
        data-anim="fade-up"
        style="transition-delay: 200ms"
      >
        Each of these industries has specific financial complexity. We know the billing structures, the compliance requirements, and the operational rhythm — because it is all we do.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div data-anim="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 300ms">
      <IndustriesAccordion client:load />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
